聆听 Duran Duran 为万圣节精心翻唱的 ELO 歌曲《Evil Woman》 https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-duran-durans-spooky-cover-of-elos-evil-woman-for-halloween-3801658?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=listen-to-万圣节杜兰杜兰斯幽灵般的埃洛斯邪恶女人封面Laura MolloyThu, 10 Oct 2024 18:22:51 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3801658 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Simon-Le-Bon-of-Duran-Duran-and-Jeff-Lynne-of-Electric-Light-Orchestra.-CREDIT_-Michael-Putland_Getty-Images-and-Fin-Costello_Redferns.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Simon-Le-Bon-of-Duran-Duran-and-Jeff-Lynne-of-Electric-Light-Orchestra.-CREDIT_-Michael-Putland_Getty-Images-and-Fin-Costello_Redferns.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Simon-Le-Bon-of-Duran-Duran-and-Jeff-Lynne-of-Electric-Light-Orchestra.-CREDIT_-Michael-Putland_Getty-Images-and-Fin-Costello_Redferns-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Simon-Le-Bon-of-Duran-Duran-and-Jeff-Lynne-of-Electric-Light-Orchestra.-CREDIT_-Michael-Putland_Getty-Images-and-Fin-Costello_Redferns-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Simon-Le-Bon-of-Duran-Duran-and-Jeff-Lynne-of-Electric-Light-Orchestra.-CREDIT_-Michael-Putland_Getty-Images-and-Fin-Costello_Redferns-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Simon-Le-Bon-of-Duran-Duran-and-Jeff-Lynne-of-Electric-Light-Orchestra.-CREDIT_-Michael-Putland_Getty-Images-and-Fin-Costello_Redferns-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Simon-Le-Bon-of-Duran-Duran-and-Jeff-Lynne-of-Electric-Light-Orchestra.-CREDIT_-Michael-Putland_Getty-Images-and-Fin-Costello_Redferns-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Duran Duran 即将开始他们的万圣节美国巡演</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-duran-durans-spooky-cover-of-elos-evil-woman-for-halloween-3801658">聆听 Duran Duran 为 ELO 万圣节创作的《Evil Woman》的怪异翻唱，</a>该帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Simon-Le-Bon-of-Duran-Duran-and-Jeff-Lynne-of-Electric-Light-Orchestra.-CREDIT_-Michael-Putland_Getty-Images-and-Fin-Costello_Redferns.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Simon-Le-Bon-of-Duran-Duran-and-Jeff-Lynne-of-Electric-Light-Orchestra.-CREDIT_-Michael-Putland_Getty-Images-and-Fin-Costello_Redferns.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Simon-Le-Bon-of-Duran-Duran-and-Jeff-Lynne-of-Electric-Light-Orchestra.-CREDIT_-Michael-Putland_Getty-Images-and-Fin-Costello_Redferns-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Simon-Le-Bon-of-Duran-Duran-and-Jeff-Lynne-of-Electric-Light-Orchestra.-CREDIT_-Michael-Putland_Getty-Images-and-Fin-Costello_Redferns-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Simon-Le-Bon-of-Duran-Duran-and-Jeff-Lynne-of-Electric-Light-Orchestra.-CREDIT_-Michael-Putland_Getty-Images-and-Fin-Costello_Redferns-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Simon-Le-Bon-of-Duran-Duran-and-Jeff-Lynne-of-Electric-Light-Orchestra.-CREDIT_-Michael-Putland_Getty-Images-and-Fin-Costello_Redferns-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Simon-Le-Bon-of-Duran-Duran-and-Jeff-Lynne-of-Electric-Light-Orchestra.-CREDIT_-Michael-Putland_Getty-Images-and-Fin-Costello_Redferns-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/duran-duran">Duran Duran</a>在万圣节前夕分享了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/electric-light-orchestra">ELO</a>的《Evil Woman》的怪异封面。看看下面。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/duran-duran-interview-2023-simon-le-bon-john-taylor-glastonbury-wet-leg-3432534">杜兰·杜兰（Duran Duran）：“我们很乐意举办格拉斯顿伯里音乐节——我们只需要合适的位置”</a></strong></li></ul><p>乐队去年分享了他们的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/duran-duran-to-cover-billie-eilish-talking-heads-on-new-halloween-themed-album-danse-macabre-3490754">万圣节主题专辑《Danse Macabre》</a> ，其中翻唱了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">Billie Eilish</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/talking-heads">Talking Heads</a>等歌曲。现在，他们宣布了“Danse Macabre – De Luxe”，这是一个扩展版本，将于明天（10 月 11 日）以数字形式发行，并于 10 月 25 日以 CD 和黑胶唱片盒形式发行。您可以<a href="https://duran.lnk.to/DanseMacabreDeluxe">在此处</a>预订/预保存。</p><p>在发行之前，他们分享了一首新的附赠曲目——翻唱了 ELO 1975 年的热门单曲，取自他们的专辑“Face the Music”。</p><p>西蒙·勒邦 (Simon Le Bon) 和同事准时到达，为恐怖季节配乐。给这首歌一种闹鬼的迪斯科感觉，伴随着振奋人心的合成合唱和迷人的弦乐。看看下面。 </p><p><iframe title="Duran Duran – 邪恶的女人（官方歌词视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/WDodrzJk5_k?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>豪华专辑中的其他内容将包括新曲目“New Moon (Dark Phase)”——由前 Duran Duran 吉他手 Andy Taylor 合作的经典曲目“New Moon on Monday”的更新翻唱——以及名为“Masque of the Pink Death”的器乐曲。 。</p><p>键盘手 Nick Rhodes 在一份新闻稿中表示：“当我们去年发行《Danse Macabre》项目时，我们自发决定制作一张庆祝万圣节疯狂和欢乐的唱片。在此过程中，我们打开了一个意想不到的好奇心和创造力的盒子，这使我们重新构思了一些旧歌曲，录制了一些我们最喜欢的歌曲的翻唱版本，并写了几首新作品。</p><p> “今年，不知何故，灵感仍然挥之不去，我喜欢扩大收藏的想法，因为我们可以……既然我们有更多的时间，为什么不添加一些我们最初考虑的歌曲呢？”他继续说道。 “这个想法催生了另一首新歌，翻唱了 ELO 经典歌曲《Evil Woman》，以及翻唱的《New Moon on Monday》。” </p><figure id="attachment_3482131" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3482131" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3482131" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/DuranDuran-Andy-Taylor-interview.jpg" alt="约翰·泰勒、西蒙·勒邦和安迪·泰勒与杜兰·杜兰一起在舞台上现场表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/DuranDuran-Andy-Taylor-interview.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/DuranDuran-Andy-Taylor-interview-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/DuranDuran-Andy-Taylor-interview-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/DuranDuran-Andy-Taylor-interview-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/DuranDuran-Andy-Taylor-interview-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/DuranDuran-Andy-Taylor-interview-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3482131" class="wp-caption-text">约翰·泰勒、西蒙·勒邦和安迪·泰勒与杜兰·杜兰一起在舞台上现场表演。图片来源：盖蒂</figcaption></figure><p>这支 80 年代的标志性乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/duran-duran-share-us-tour-dates-for-2024-buy-tickets-3773106">即将开始他们的万圣节美国巡演</a>，巡演将于 10 月 21 日在宾夕法尼亚州阿伦敦举行演出。请<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/duran-duran-share-us-tour-dates-for-2024-buy-tickets-3773106">在此处</a>查看完整的日期列表，并<a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Fduran-duran-tickets%2Fartist%2F734969" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>查找任何剩余的门票。</p><p>在 Duran Duran 的其他新闻中，今年早些时候有报道称，该乐队的主唱<a style="font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/roxy-musics-phil-manzanera-and-duran-durans-simon-le-bon-among-kings-birthday-honours-list-3765954">Simon Le Bon 是今年国王生日荣誉名单中的娱乐人物之一</a>。</p><p>他因其对音乐和慈善事业的贡献而被授予大英帝国勋章，这一消息是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-model-from-duran-durans-rio-cover-has-finally-been-identified-3764932">在该乐队《Rio》专辑封面上的模特最终被确定为玛西娅·亨特（现称为玛西·丁克尔）</a>几天后宣布的。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Duran Duran 谈新音乐《Wet Leg》和他们的格拉斯顿伯里梦想 |谈话中" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/-B-IVaTCP3k?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/duran-duran-interview-2023-simon-le-bon-john-taylor-glastonbury-wet-leg-3432534">去年， <em>NME</em>还采访了 Duran Duran</a> ，他们在会上谈到了参加<a href="https://www.nme.com/glastonbury">格拉斯顿伯里音乐节的</a>渴望。令人惊讶的是，乐队从未在沃西农场举办的大型音乐节上演出， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-line-up-set-times-stage-splits-3749871#:~:text=Glastonbury%20will%20return%20to%20Worthy,See%20the%20schedule%20below.">该音乐节将于今年 6 月 26 日至 30 日回归</a>。</p><p>主唱西蒙·勒邦 (Simon Le Bon) 在接受<em>NME</em>采访时表示：“我很乐意（这样做）——我们只需要获得合适的位置，仅此而已。</p><p> “我们以前有过这样的机会，但当时没有在主舞台上表演，我想我们肯定愿意这样做。我确信我们正在（与格拉斯顿伯里）进行谈判，如果没有，我们也会这样做。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-duran-durans-spooky-cover-of-elos-evil-woman-for-halloween-3801658">聆听 Duran Duran 为 ELO 万圣节创作的《Evil Woman》的怪异翻唱，</a>该帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
安德鲁·加菲尔德认为性爱场景已经改变，因为“我们在现实生活中彼此建立的联系越来越少” https://www.nme.com/news/film/andrew-garfield-thinks-sex-scenes-have-changed-because-we-are-building-less-connection-with-each-other-in-our- real-lives-3801659?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=andrew-garfield-thinks-sex-scene-have-changed-because-we-rebuilding-less-connection-with-each-other-in-our-real-生活Chris EdwardsThu, 10 Oct 2024 18:01:50 +0000 Film NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3801659 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Andrew-Garfield.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Andrew-Garfield.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Andrew-Garfield-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Andrew-Garfield-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Andrew-Garfield-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Andrew-Garfield-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Andrew-Garfield-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我们与现实的距离要远得多”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/andrew-garfield-thinks-sex-scenes-have-changed-because-we-are-building-less-connection-with-each-other-in-our-real-lives-3801659">安德鲁·加菲尔德 (Andrew Garfield) 认为性爱场景已经发生变化，因为“我们在现实生活中彼此之间建立的联系越来越少”，</a>该帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Andrew-Garfield.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Andrew-Garfield.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Andrew-Garfield-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Andrew-Garfield-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Andrew-Garfield-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Andrew-Garfield-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Andrew-Garfield-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/andrew-garfield">安德鲁·加菲尔德</a>谈到了他的新片《<em>我们生活在时间》</em>中的性爱场景，以及为什么这种亲密的描绘在现代电影中变得罕见。</p><p>这部催人泪下的非线性爱情故事根据尼克·佩恩的剧本改编，讲述了托拜厄斯（加菲猫饰）和阿尔穆特（<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/florence-pugh">弗洛伦斯·皮尤饰</a>）在长达十年的恋爱关系中经历的一些极端的高潮和低谷。</p><p>这部电影有一些沉重、有趣、出汗和简单现实的性爱场景，加菲猫同意这些场景已经变得不那么常见了。 “现在你已经看不到那么多了，”他在与导演约翰·克劳利的联合采访中告诉<a href="https://www.indiewire.com/features/interviews/andrew-garfield-john-crowley-we-live-in-time-boy-a-interview-1235054811/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>IndieWire</em></a> 。</p><p> “我想这部电影可能给人一种来自不同时代的感觉，因为我们现在对彼此更加警惕，”加菲尔德继续说道。 “偏执狂。已删除。孤立。分开了。因为这些东西，亲密感少了很多。</p><p> “我们与自己的亲密程度要低得多，我们与死亡的亲密程度也要低得多。我们的感受。现实。事实上，我们与现实的距离要远得多。我们现在体验世界的方式存在着一种分歧，我认为这就是一部充满渴望的电影。”</p><p>他补充道：“我认为观众对这些图像要么是无意识的，要么是有意识的渴望。我认为，在屏幕上看到这种程度的亲密和联系，对人们来说将是一个可爱的提醒和启发。” </p><figure id="attachment_3412930" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3412930" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3412930" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Andrew-Garfield-main-new.jpg" alt="安德鲁·加菲尔德" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Andrew-Garfield-main-new.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Andrew-Garfield-main-new-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Andrew-Garfield-main-new-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Andrew-Garfield-main-new-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Andrew-Garfield-main-new-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Andrew-Garfield-main-new-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3412930" class="wp-caption-text">安德鲁·加菲尔德。图片来源：Cindy Ord/VF23/Getty Images for Vanity Fair</figcaption></figure><p>对于为什么类似的性爱场景变得罕见，克劳利提出了自己的看法，他建议：“我想知道这是否与性爱场景有点乏味有关，感觉它们是情节的机械功能。</p><p> “我喜欢《托拜厄斯和阿尔穆特》的地方在于，因为它是五年婚姻的完整写照，所以你会看到两种截然不同的亲密场景：当他们第一次冲进门时（在他们的初恋场景中） 】，而且他们的手不能离开对方，然后是后期，预处理，这要微妙得多。但在这两种情况下，最美妙的是他们在场景中都没有失去幽默感。”</p><p>上周，加菲猫承认<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/andrew-garfield-says-he-is-unlikely-to-appear-in-the-social-network-sequel-3799457">他不太可能出现在即将上映的<em>《社交网络》</em>续集中</a>，因为他曾出演过 2010 年的原版 Facebook 投资人爱德华多·萨维林 (Eduardo Saverin)。</p><p>不过，他确实表示，他将在未来的项目中“100%” <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/andrew-garfield-says-he-would-100-per-cent-reprise-spider-man-role-3799268">再次扮演<em>蜘蛛侠</em>的角色</a>。</p><p> <strong>《我们生活在时光》将于 2025 年 1 月 1 日在英国和爱尔兰各地影院上映。</strong></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/andrew-garfield-thinks-sex-scenes-have-changed-because-we-are-building-less-connection-with-each-other-in-our-real-lives-3801659">安德鲁·加菲尔德 (Andrew Garfield) 认为性爱场景已经发生变化，因为“我们在现实生活中彼此之间建立的联系越来越少”，</a>该帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
